title: Staying Committed | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Staying Committed | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to receive everything God has prepared for you, you can’t give up on what you’re believing for. Stay in faith. What He promised will come to pass.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
